were

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:18.630
acting like. And I remember in these

00:21:18.640 --> 00:21:21.910
visions I saw it, but it was by design.

00:21:21.920 --> 00:21:26.710
When they came, I saw tent cities,

00:21:26.720 --> 00:21:28.550
so much so that there were tent cities

00:21:28.560 --> 00:21:30.230
like Skid Row

00:21:30.240 --> 00:21:31.790
and people were all over the place, but

00:21:31.800 --> 00:21:34.350
revival broke out.

00:21:34.350 --> 00:21:34.360
I've

00:21:34.360 --> 00:21:36.750
talked about this for several

00:21:36.760 --> 00:21:38.990
years telling Brad, "I see

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:41.670
fields full of people

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:43.590
coming here trying to get a better

00:21:43.600 --> 00:21:45.590
life, but then they don't have enough to

00:21:45.600 --> 00:21:47.510
get here."They are broke,

00:21:47.520 --> 00:21:49.270
and the finances and all the things that

00:21:49.280 --> 00:21:51.110
I have told about the

00:21:51.110 --> 00:21:51.120
finances—praying

00:21:51.120 --> 00:21:52.830
now, I've already talked too

00:21:52.840 --> 00:21:54.350
long;

00:21:54.360 --> 00:21:56.710
28 minutes. But

00:21:58.760 --> 00:22:00.870
I just think it's interesting as we see

00:22:00.880 --> 00:22:03.470
these things happening on the news.

00:22:03.480 --> 00:22:05.390
Talk show people are talking

00:22:05.400 --> 00:22:07.350
about what's going on.

00:22:07.360 --> 00:22:09.790
And then one sister told us, "You

00:22:09.800 --> 00:22:11.670
have no idea. I live in Europe and

00:22:11.680 --> 00:22:13.910
you're not hearing what's truly

00:22:13.920 --> 00:22:15.470
happening

00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:18.470
in our country through your media.

00:22:18.480 --> 00:22:21.030
You're being censored

00:22:21.040 --> 00:22:23.590
to the point where you are truly not

00:22:23.600 --> 00:22:25.230
hearing what's going on in other parts

00:22:25.240 --> 00:22:26.590
of the

00:22:26.590 --> 00:22:26.600
world."What

00:22:26.600 --> 00:22:29.270
do we not see through CNN, Fox,

00:22:29.280 --> 00:22:31.710
ABC, NBC, and wire news channels that we

00:22:31.720 --> 00:22:33.230
don't see on X or whatever? I'm

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:35.390
thinking, "Is that true?"So, if that is

00:22:35.400 --> 00:22:36.830
true and you are in these other

00:22:36.840 --> 00:22:38.550
countries and you say, "Brandon, you all

00:22:38.560 --> 00:22:40.030
are clueless. What's going on over here?

00:22:40.040 --> 00:22:42.070
We live in Africa. Tell us."Tell us in

00:22:42.080 --> 00:22:43.990
the comments down below. Say,

00:22:43.990 --> 00:22:44.000
"Y'all

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:45.990
aren't here. You really don't know truly

00:22:46.000 --> 00:22:48.310
what's going on in Asia. You truly don't

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:51.390
know what's going on in Africa or

00:22:51.400 --> 00:22:53.430
South America. You all are

00:22:53.440 --> 00:22:55.510
clueless what's going on in Venezuela

00:22:55.520 --> 00:22:57.550
right now because your media is not

00:22:57.560 --> 00:22:59.990
telling you."And if that's true, tell us because

00:22:59.990 --> 00:23:00.000
I'm

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:02.550
curious. We get these emails

00:23:02.560 --> 00:23:04.470
and I'm thinking, "Are these people

00:23:04.480 --> 00:23:06.630
just pulling our

00:23:06.640 --> 00:23:08.590
chain?"We

00:23:08.600 --> 00:23:10.550
get a lot of emails from all around

00:23:10.560 --> 00:23:12.310
the world all the time. Diana is

00:23:12.320 --> 00:23:13.950
continually telling me, "Did you know

00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:15.790
this is going on in this country and

00:23:15.800 --> 00:23:17.270
all this?"And I'm going,

00:23:17.270 --> 00:23:17.280
"Wow."I

00:23:17.280 --> 00:23:19.750
realize I have so many

00:23:19.760 --> 00:23:21.190
people following me from all around the

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:23.190
world. So,

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:25.190
we're just old

00:23:25.200 --> 00:23:26.870
country people in Oklahoma. We don't

00:23:26.880 --> 00:23:29.350
know. But it's interesting because

00:23:29.360 --> 00:23:31.510
there's so many of you from all

00:23:31.520 --> 00:23:33.790
over the place. Let's

00:23:33.800 --> 00:23:36.750
pray. I'll give you

00:23:36.760 --> 00:23:40.390
just five minutes here. I saw

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:44.110
Cuba a lot last night. I saw sniffers.

00:23:44.120 --> 00:23:45.710
And when people say, "What is a

00:23:45.710 --> 00:23:45.720
sniffer?"It

00:23:45.720 --> 00:23:48.710
was airplanes sniffing for

00:23:48.720 --> 00:23:51.670
atomic bombs—nuclear. I saw these

00:23:51.680 --> 00:23:53.070
sniffers going throughout... I

00:23:53.080 --> 00:23:55.830
saw sniffers that were on poles in

00:23:55.840 --> 00:23:58.710
major cities in Boston and these other

00:23:58.720 --> 00:24:00.070
areas.

00:24:00.080 --> 00:24:03.830
I saw that they had a way of being

00:24:03.840 --> 00:24:06.390
able to detect backpacks

00:24:06.390 --> 00:24:06.400
and

00:24:06.400 --> 00:24:10.350
suitcases,

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:10.360
using

00:24:10.360 --> 00:24:13.750
some kind of sensor.

00:24:13.760 --> 00:24:16.470
It was able to sniff

00:24:16.470 --> 00:24:16.480
them.

00:24:16.480 --> 00:24:17.550
And that's what I was talking about. I'm not

00:24:17.560 --> 00:24:18.950
trying to be weird saying, 'Well, you're

00:24:18.960 --> 00:24:21.070
sniffing things.'No, that's what

00:24:21.080 --> 00:24:23.430
the Lord called it. It was

00:24:23.440 --> 00:24:24.870
sniffing.

00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:26.310
Now,

00:24:26.320 --> 00:24:28.790
like I said, I saw it. It looked like a

00:24:28.800 --> 00:24:31.430
big plane with a

00:24:31.440 --> 00:24:35.510
big nose, and it

00:24:35.520 --> 00:24:37.790
was an actual flesh human nose on a

00:24:37.800 --> 00:24:40.310
plane sniffing the land and the

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:42.590
areas. I knew that was a

00:24:42.600 --> 00:24:44.790
symbolization of something, and that's

00:24:44.800 --> 00:24:46.150
why I said I don't know. I tell him

00:24:46.160 --> 00:24:47.990
I've seen a plane sniffing

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:50.910
things.

00:24:50.920 --> 00:24:53.190
I see a plane flying through the

00:24:53.200 --> 00:24:56.750
atmosphere trying to sniff things. I see

00:24:56.760 --> 00:24:59.870
poles and electronics sniffing

00:24:59.880 --> 00:25:01.950
things.

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:03.550
And the Lord said, 'This is not real

00:25:03.560 --> 00:25:04.950
sniffing.

00:25:04.960 --> 00:25:09.190
This is a detecting early alert

00:25:09.190 --> 00:25:09.200
system.'I

00:25:09.200 --> 00:25:15.750
saw Fidel Castro during the old Cold War

00:25:15.760 --> 00:25:19.310
last night, and I saw that he was given a

00:25:19.320 --> 00:25:22.070
weapon of mass destruction

00:25:22.080 --> 00:25:24.910
that they have hidden for decades from

00:25:24.920 --> 00:25:26.470
Russia.

00:25:26.480 --> 00:25:29.110
It was the Cuban

00:25:29.120 --> 00:25:30.990
Missile Crisis;

00:25:31.000 --> 00:25:33.670
it looked like a briefcase.

00:25:33.680 --> 00:25:35.710
It looked like some kind of thing that

00:25:35.720 --> 00:25:38.270
they were trying to hide

00:25:38.270 --> 00:25:38.280
underground

00:25:38.280 --> 00:25:43.070
in a mountain in Cuba,

00:25:43.080 --> 00:25:45.110
trying to cover it with

00:25:45.120 --> 00:25:47.470
some kind of metal.

00:25:47.480 --> 00:25:49.550
I kept hearing,

00:25:52.400 --> 00:25:53.910
'Don't go at this with pride.

00:25:57.640 --> 00:25:59.830
Don't go at this with

00:25:59.840 --> 00:26:01.670
pride, for they have something secret

00:26:01.680 --> 00:26:04.910
inside.

00:26:04.920 --> 00:26:06.990
Don't be prideful. Don't

00:26:07.000 --> 00:26:09.230
underestimate your

00:26:09.240 --> 00:26:12.790
enemy.'I

00:26:12.800 --> 00:26:15.070
saw lead,

00:26:15.080 --> 00:26:16.470
and the Lord was showing me there's

00:26:16.480 --> 00:26:18.230
something about lead they

00:26:18.230 --> 00:26:18.240
used

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:20.950
to hide this thing so it would not be

00:26:20.960 --> 00:26:23.310
detected through

00:26:23.320 --> 00:26:25.430
metal and mud. I don't understand it

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:28.310
all. I am just seeing this in part, hearing

00:26:28.310 --> 00:26:28.320
in

00:26:28.320 --> 00:26:29.510
part.

00:26:29.520 --> 00:26:34.430
But I saw these brass hands

00:26:34.440 --> 00:26:37.910
that looked like giant hands, massive

00:26:37.920 --> 00:26:40.630
fingers like

00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:43.150
Fantastic Four,

00:26:43.160 --> 00:26:44.110
the

00:26:44.120 --> 00:26:47.270
rock guy—the way his body was

00:26:47.280 --> 00:26:50.590
rock. These fingers

00:26:50.600 --> 00:26:53.550
looked like rock, but they were

00:26:53.560 --> 00:26:56.030
brass.

00:26:56.040 --> 00:26:59.350
And the brass went up

00:26:59.360 --> 00:27:01.430
like a bowl.

00:27:01.440 --> 00:27:03.470
'That's it, son. Just like those hands.

00:27:03.480 --> 00:27:04.750
Do you see those?

00:27:04.760 --> 00:27:07.683
Show those

00:27:07.693 --> 00:27:08.350
hands.'They

00:27:08.360 --> 00:27:11.230
were that big,

00:27:11.240 --> 00:27:13.550
that thick. These big rock-looking

00:27:13.560 --> 00:27:16.590
fingers were brass

00:27:16.600 --> 00:27:19.670
and they went up like

00:27:19.680 --> 00:27:22.670
a massive bowl,

00:27:22.680 --> 00:27:25.870
formed around like a cup. And in

00:27:25.880 --> 00:27:28.630
the middle of the palm of the

00:27:28.640 --> 00:27:30.430
hand,

00:27:30.440 --> 00:27:33.070
Marco Rubio was standing there

00:27:33.070 --> 00:27:33.080
in

00:27:33.080 --> 00:27:37.350
a suit.

00:27:37.360 --> 00:27:41.430
I saw these hands embracing him;

00:27:41.440 --> 00:27:43.110
they looked like brass,

00:27:43.120 --> 00:27:45.270
shiny,

00:27:45.280 --> 00:27:46.830
and it was concerning

00:27:46.840 --> 00:27:48.990
Cuba.

00:27:49.000 --> 00:27:51.790
As he was standing there,

00:27:51.800 --> 00:27:53.030
the Lord said, 'This is personal to

00:27:53.040 --> 00:27:56.230
him.'I

00:27:56.240 --> 00:28:00.430
saw it was personal. I saw relatives,

00:28:00.440 --> 00:28:03.350
people that meant something to him

00:28:03.350 --> 00:28:03.360
who

00:28:03.360 --> 00:28:04.350
were

00:28:04.360 --> 00:28:06.590
attached to Cuba.

00:28:06.600 --> 00:28:08.710
I saw him rise up and I saw a

00:28:08.720 --> 00:28:12.710
liberation coming to the Cuban people.

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:16.550
I saw our military, certain

00:28:16.550 --> 00:28:16.560
units

00:28:16.560 --> 00:28:18.830
with crosses that were

00:28:18.840 --> 00:28:21.830
symbolic to this. Now, I'm not going all

00:28:21.840 --> 00:28:23.190
into this

00:28:23.200 --> 00:28:24.990
for a reason. There's a lot of you

00:28:24.990 --> 00:28:25.000
who

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:26.270
will never make it to the end of

00:28:26.270 --> 00:28:26.280
this

00:28:26.280 --> 00:28:28.550
video.

00:28:28.560 --> 00:28:30.790
I'm not trying to

00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:32.670
be snide; I'm saying there was a

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:34.390
reason why the Lord waited until

00:28:34.390 --> 00:28:34.400
many

00:28:34.400 --> 00:28:35.790
of you left.

00:28:35.800 --> 00:28:38.030
But

00:28:38.040 --> 00:28:40.630
I try to give you what I feel in

00:28:40.640 --> 00:28:42.270
my spirit,

00:28:42.270 --> 00:28:42.280
too.

00:28:42.280 --> 00:28:43.990
If you want to pray with it, pray.

00:28:50.800 --> 00:28:54.830
I saw these hands. I saw

00:28:54.830 --> 00:28:54.840
that

00:28:54.840 --> 00:28:58.630
the guy who was over it had

00:29:01.840 --> 00:29:04.630
chemical

00:29:04.640 --> 00:29:06.990
warfare

00:29:06.990 --> 00:29:07.000
weapons

00:29:07.000 --> 00:29:09.310
for viruses

00:29:09.310 --> 00:29:09.320
that,

00:29:09.320 --> 00:29:12.070
when people got them, they got

00:29:12.080 --> 00:29:16.630
these big sores on their

00:29:16.630 --> 00:29:16.640
bodies

00:29:16.640 --> 00:29:19.990
that looked like fire ant

00:29:19.990 --> 00:29:20.000
bites,

00:29:20.000 --> 00:29:23.750
round

00:29:23.760 --> 00:29:25.870
like a

00:29:25.880 --> 00:29:27.910
half dollar. Some were

00:29:27.920 --> 00:29:32.750
sores and boils all over the body,

00:29:32.760 --> 00:29:35.910
full of white infection with

00:29:35.910 --> 00:29:35.920
a

00:29:35.920 --> 00:29:40.190
black center.

00:29:40.200 --> 00:29:41.830
It was nasty.

00:29:41.840 --> 00:29:44.270
I don't know if

00:29:44.280 --> 00:29:46.430
this was smallpox.

00:29:47.640 --> 00:29:51.030
But I saw a canister

00:29:51.040 --> 00:29:54.950
that looked like a cylinder

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:58.070
with a biohazard symbol on the

00:29:58.080 --> 00:30:00.430
side.

00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:02.990
As I was praying, I heard

00:30:02.990 --> 00:30:03.000
'burros'.

00:30:03.000 --> 00:30:05.310
Burro—Braden

00:30:05.320 --> 00:30:09.310
said 'burro'means donkey.

00:30:10.680 --> 00:30:12.350
As we were praying in

00:30:12.360 --> 00:30:14.870
Spanish, the Lord showed us about

00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:17.670
mules in the night. I saw the

00:30:17.680 --> 00:30:21.790
American Coast Guard with radar

00:30:21.800 --> 00:30:22.710
on the

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:25.190
tip of

00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:28.390
their boat, spinning around, able to

00:30:28.400 --> 00:30:31.190
detect if there was trouble in the

00:30:31.200 --> 00:30:32.590
water

00:30:32.600 --> 00:30:34.470
coming towards America.

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:37.990
I saw the United States Coast Guard

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:41.230
heavily patrolling Florida,

00:30:41.240 --> 00:30:44.390
and they were not able to penetrate the

00:30:44.400 --> 00:30:47.550
patrol like they were when Joe Biden was

00:30:47.560 --> 00:30:51.750
here. Thank God for President Trump.

00:30:51.760 --> 00:30:53.270
I saw

00:30:53.280 --> 00:30:56.390
these patrol boats really doing their

00:30:56.400 --> 00:30:57.750
jobs.

00:30:57.760 --> 00:31:00.670
They knew they couldn't get past

00:31:00.680 --> 00:31:04.590
our first defenses,

00:31:04.600 --> 00:31:07.150
so they were trying to devise a plan.

00:31:07.160 --> 00:31:08.990
But the Lord said they don't have

00:31:09.000 --> 00:31:13.030
weapons like Iran does.

00:31:13.040 --> 00:31:15.070
The rockets

00:31:15.080 --> 00:31:18.150
I saw didn't have the capability

00:31:18.160 --> 00:31:22.670
to strap a payload like Iran would;

00:31:22.680 --> 00:31:24.550
they didn't have the ability to strike

00:31:24.560 --> 00:31:26.990
America like Iran.

00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:27.990
Now,

00:31:28.000 --> 00:31:29.350
if I'm wrong, I'm wrong. But that's what

00:31:29.360 --> 00:31:30.870
I saw.

00:31:30.880 --> 00:31:32.150
Now, you say, 'Well, Brandon, they

00:31:32.160 --> 00:31:32.990
do.'I

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:34.790
saw that they didn't.

00:31:34.800 --> 00:31:37.310
If they do, then I missed it.

00:31:37.320 --> 00:31:39.230
But I'm telling you what I saw

00:31:39.240 --> 00:31:40.990
in the vision.

00:31:45.840 --> 00:31:49.510
I saw our

00:31:49.520 --> 00:31:51.190
heroes—our

00:31:51.200 --> 00:31:53.310
men and

00:31:53.320 --> 00:31:55.350
women that protect our nation. God bless

00:31:55.360 --> 00:31:57.990
them. The Lord said,

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:59.350
'Pray for

00:31:59.350 --> 00:31:59.360
them.'That's

00:31:59.360 --> 00:32:01.270
all I will say.

00:32:05.310 --> 00:32:05.320
And

00:32:10.160 --> 00:32:12.870
I saw cyberattacks coming to Cuba in

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:14.830
the darkness again.

00:32:14.840 --> 00:32:16.950
I saw

00:32:16.960 --> 00:32:19.510
a liberation and the Lord said, 'Do

00:32:19.520 --> 00:32:21.630
this by surprise and keep your mouth

00:32:21.640 --> 00:32:25.270
shut, leadership,

00:32:25.280 --> 00:32:29.710
for don't underestimate your

00:32:29.710 --> 00:32:29.720
enemy.'Announcing

00:32:29.720 --> 00:32:32.110
things and too much chatter

00:32:32.120 --> 00:32:36.070
is not healthy for the people going in,

00:32:36.080 --> 00:32:38.470
the ones risking their lives as

00:32:38.480 --> 00:32:40.230
you sit behind a desk pushing

00:32:40.230 --> 00:32:40.240
a

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:42.510
button.

00:32:43.960 --> 00:32:45.030
Be

00:32:45.040 --> 00:32:47.430
still. Pray for them.

00:32:47.440 --> 00:32:49.950
I saw the chatter in the

00:32:49.960 --> 00:32:53.750
still of the night, like in Venezuela.

00:32:53.760 --> 00:32:55.270
The Lord said, 'Watch this. Pray for

00:32:55.280 --> 00:32:56.350
them.'But

00:32:56.360 --> 00:32:58.750
out of retaliation,

00:32:58.760 --> 00:33:01.230
that which was in the mountain was used

00:33:01.240 --> 00:33:03.870
upon the land.

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:08.430
The guy in Cuba is

00:33:08.430 --> 00:33:08.440
nuts—the

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:09.790
leader.

00:33:09.800 --> 00:33:13.150
I saw a mountain glow with a ripple

00:33:13.160 --> 00:33:15.790
of a wave that looked like

00:33:15.800 --> 00:33:18.510
an atom bomb. It went straight up and

00:33:18.520 --> 00:33:21.150
off the side of a mountain

00:33:21.160 --> 00:33:25.070
in retaliation to him

00:33:25.080 --> 00:33:28.350
losing his position.

00:33:28.360 --> 00:33:30.110
I thought, surely he wouldn't do that

00:33:30.120 --> 00:33:34.350
to his own people.

00:33:34.360 --> 00:33:37.390
But it was on the side of a mountain,

00:33:37.390 --> 00:33:37.400
looking

00:33:37.400 --> 00:33:39.030
like a

00:33:39.040 --> 00:33:42.030
mushroom cloud.

00:33:42.040 --> 00:33:44.990
I saw Fidel Castro's face

00:33:46.830 --> 00:33:46.840
and

00:33:48.960 --> 00:33:51.310
his beard. The Lord said he

00:33:51.320 --> 00:33:55.070
got this weapon back when he was in

00:33:55.080 --> 00:33:56.150
power

00:33:56.160 --> 00:33:57.910
and he's had it the whole

00:33:57.920 --> 00:33:59.230
time.

00:34:01.120 --> 00:34:04.590
It was a trade

00:34:04.600 --> 00:34:07.710
with

00:34:07.720 --> 00:34:11.230
Russia—I

